OL,4,Cbreach over NI special education
OL,5,Cspreadsheet
OL,7,FThe Department of Education in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland is investigating a
OL,9,Fdata leak after a spreadsheet was sent
OL,10,Fin error to 174 people.
OL,12,FIt came about when those individuals
OL,13,Fregistered interest for an event about
OL,14,Fthe End-to End Review of Special
OL,15,FEducational Needs (SEN).
