OL,5,Cspreadsheet
OL,7,FThe department said they received in
OL,8,Ferror a spreadsheet containing the
OL,9,Fnames, email address and titles of 407
OL,10,Findividuals who had expressed an
OL,11,Finterest in attending the End-to End
OL,12,FReview of SEN events across Northern
OL,13,FIreland.
OL,15,FThe spreadsheet also included comments
OL,16,Fmade by a number of individuals.
