OL,7,FThe department said the 174
OL,8,Findividuals who received the personal
OL,9,Fdata in error have been asked to
OL,10,Fdelete the information and confirm
OL,11,Fthey have done so.
OL,13,FEducation Minister Paul Givan said his
OL,14,Fdepartment is investigating the
OL,15,Fcircumstances surrounding the data
OL,16,Fbreach on Thursday and apologised to
OL,17,Fall affected.
