OL,7,F"The department takes its
OL,8,Fresponsibilities around data
OL,9,Fprotection extremely seriously and we
OL,10,Funreservedly apologise to all those
OL,11,Faffected as this should not have
OL,12,Fhappened," he said.
OL,14,F"The individuals involved have been
OL,15,Fcontacted to make them aware of the
OL,16,Fdata breach."
