OL,7,FMr Givan said he has instructed his
OL,8,FPermanent Secretary to launch a full
OL,9,Fand thorough investigation into the
OL,10,Fdata breach which will be led by
OL,11,FInternal Audit.
OL,13,F"In parallel, the department will be
OL,14,Fworking to put in place measures to
OL,15,Fhelp make sure this does not happen
OL,16,Fagain," he said.
